13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1607, as
15 amended by Section 1, Chapter 26, O.S.L. 2024 (59 O.S. Supp. 2024,
16 Section 1607), is amended to read as follows:
17 Section 1607. A. There is hereby re-created, to continue until
18 July 1, 2027, in accordance with the provisions of the Oklahoma
19 Sunset Law, the Board of Examiners for Speech-Language Pathology and
20 Audiology whose duty it is to administer the provisions of the
21 Speech-Language Pathology and Audiology Licensing Act. The members
22 of the Board shall be residents of this state and shall be appointed
23 by the Governor with the advice and consent of the Senate. The
24 Board shall be composed of five (5) members consisting of three
